# Dummy pacman packages for the mingw DB.
# Each name becomes an empty pacman package so makepkg's dep checker
# is satisfied. These are build tools / MSYS2-layer deps provided by
# Fedora (or not needed for cross-compilation).
#
# Non-prefixed names are MSYS2-layer host tools (git, groff, etc.).
# Prefixed names (mingw-w64-ucrt-x86_64-*) are MINGW deps that are
# either provided by the host (python, cmake) or not applicable to
# cross-compilation (clang, emscripten).

# MSYS2-layer host tools
autoconf-archive
docbook-xsl
git
groff
po4a
xmlto

# Build tools — provided by Fedora
mingw-w64-ucrt-x86_64-asciidoc
mingw-w64-ucrt-x86_64-asciidoctor
